                     <handNote scope="major" script="nasta_liq" medium="ink">
                        Primarily written in <material>black</material> nasta‘līq with <material>red</material> subheaders by <persName role="scr">Ḥamzah ibn Umah</persName>, who possibly likely also wrote a majority of the marginal commentaries.
                     </handNote>
